CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 15, 1962, pg. 17 reads: "Beautiful Yard Awards Program - Cultivators of above-average yards in Homewood attended the seventh annual awards program and tea sponsored by the Homewood Community Improvement Association...The Westinghouse Octet, pictured in the right-center photo, furnished the music...-Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of the Westinghouse Octet, including Mike Turner left rear, Ulyesses Boyd far right, and two women wearing choir robes, standing in Bethesda United Presbyterian Church during seventh annual beautiful yard awards program
